{"chunk_id": "bank_enterprise_amount_mismatch_playbook_001", "source_name": "银企对账金额差异处理公开规则摘要", "source_url": "https://www.gov.cn/gongbao/content/2006/content_375800.htm", "source_file": "data/rag/raw_sources/bank_enterprise/bank_enterprise_amount_mismatch_playbook.md", "source_type": "policy_summary", "section_title": "双边金额差异识别", "page_no": null, "element_type": "paragraph", "business_tags": ["amount_mismatch", "bank_enterprise", "audit_trail"], "content": "银企对账中，银行流水与企业账簿均存在同一业务标识，但借贷方向、入账金额或手续费拆分后净额不一致，应归为金额差异。处理时需要同时保留银行端金额、企业端金额、差异金额和原始币种，不能只保留折算后的单一金额。\n\n本项目抽象规则：`AMOUNT_MISMATCH` 对应 `BE-R002`，必须进入待复核链路并带出双边金额字段。"}
{"chunk_id": "bank_enterprise_amount_mismatch_playbook_002", "source_name": "银企对账金额差异处理公开规则摘要", "source_url": "https://www.gov.cn/gongbao/content/2006/content_375800.htm", "source_file": "data/rag/raw_sources/bank_enterprise/bank_enterprise_amount_mismatch_playbook.md", "source_type": "policy_summary", "section_title": "手续费和净额拆分", "page_no": null, "element_type": "paragraph", "business_tags": ["amount_mismatch", "bank_enterprise", "audit_trail"], "content": "企业账簿可能按交易金额、手续费和净额分录，银行流水可能只体现实际入账或扣款金额。金额差异复核时应先核对手续费字段、交易方向和摘要，再判断是否属于费用拆分造成的表面差异。\n\n本项目抽象规则：若差异来自手续费拆分，证据应包含手续费金额、交易金额和净额，不得直接自动平账。"}
{"chunk_id": "bank_enterprise_amount_mismatch_playbook_003", "source_name": "银企对账金额差异处理公开规则摘要", "source_url": "https://www.gov.cn/gongbao/content/2006/content_375800.htm", "source_file": "data/rag/raw_sources/bank_enterprise/bank_enterprise_amount_mismatch_playbook.md", "source_type": "policy_summary", "section_title": "方向反记金额不平", "page_no": null, "element_type": "paragraph", "business_tags": ["amount_mismatch", "bank_enterprise", "audit_trail"], "content": "同一业务在银行端表现为借方，在企业账簿中误记为贷方，或相反方向入账，会造成金额符号不一致。此类异常要同时记录方向、绝对金额和原始分录说明。\n\n本项目抽象规则：金额方向不一致仍归入 `AMOUNT_MISMATCH`，审计意见需提示检查借贷方向。"}
{"chunk_id": "bank_enterprise_amount_mismatch_playbook_004", "source_name": "银企对账金额差异处理公开规则摘要", "source_url": "https://www.gov.cn/gongbao/content/2006/content_375800.htm", "source_file": "data/rag/raw_sources/bank_enterprise/bank_enterprise_amount_mismatch_playbook.md", "source_type": "policy_summary", "section_title": "部分付款或拆分到账", "page_no": null, "element_type": "paragraph", "business_tags": ["amount_mismatch", "bank_enterprise", "audit_trail"], "content": "客户付款可能被拆成多笔到账，企业账簿可能按合同或发票做一笔总账。若同一业务标识下存在部分金额匹配、部分金额缺口，应保留匹配部分和剩余差额。\n\n本项目抽象规则：不能用单笔相近金额推断已平账，应输出差异金额和待核对的拆分线索。"}
{"chunk_id": "bank_enterprise_amount_mismatch_playbook_005", "source_name": "银企对账金额差异处理公开规则摘要", "source_url": "https://www.gov.cn/gongbao/content/2006/content_375800.htm", "source_file": "data/rag/raw_sources/bank_enterprise/bank_enterprise_amount_mismatch_playbook.md", "source_type": "policy_summary", "section_title": "舍入和币种折算差异", "page_no": null, "element_type": "paragraph", "business_tags": ["amount_mismatch", "bank_enterprise", "audit_trail"], "content": "跨币种或系统间舍入规则不同，可能导致小额尾差。尾差处理仍应保留汇率、折算日期、原币金额和本币金额，经过规则或人工确认后才能闭环。\n\n本项目抽象规则：小额尾差需要 evidence 支持；RAG 无命中时必须转人工。"}
{"chunk_id": "bank_enterprise_bank_unarrived_playbook_001", "source_name": "银行未达账处理公开规则摘要", "source_url": "https://www.pbc.gov.cn/eportal/fileDir/history_file/files/att_19041_2.pdf", "source_file": "data/rag/raw_sources/bank_enterprise/bank_enterprise_bank_unarrived_playbook.md", "source_type": "policy_summary", "section_title": "企业已记银行未达", "page_no": null, "element_type": "paragraph", "business_tags": ["bank_unarrived", "bank_enterprise", "query_reply"], "content": "企业账簿已有收付款记录，但银行流水暂未出现对应入账或扣款时，应识别为银行未达账。处理时要保留企业凭证号、记账日期、金额和预计银行入账渠道。\n\n本项目抽象规则：`BANK_UNARRIVED` 对应 `BE-R005`，不能以企业单侧记录直接确认平账。"}
{"chunk_id": "bank_enterprise_bank_unarrived_playbook_002", "source_name": "银行未达账处理公开规则摘要", "source_url": "https://www.pbc.gov.cn/eportal/fileDir/history_file/files/att_19041_2.pdf", "source_file": "data/rag/raw_sources/bank_enterprise/bank_enterprise_bank_unarrived_playbook.md", "source_type": "policy_summary", "section_title": "在途交易时间窗口", "page_no": null, "element_type": "paragraph", "business_tags": ["bank_unarrived", "bank_enterprise", "query_reply"], "content": "跨行转账、批量代发、节假日或渠道清算延迟，可能造成企业已记账但银行次日才入账。复核应关注交易发起时间、清算日期和银行入账截止时间。\n\n本项目抽象规则：若存在 T+1 或在途线索，审计意见需要提示后续追溯或次日复查。"}
{"chunk_id": "bank_enterprise_bank_unarrived_playbook_003", "source_name": "银行未达账处理公开规则摘要", "source_url": "https://www.pbc.gov.cn/eportal/fileDir/history_file/files/att_19041_2.pdf", "source_file": "data/rag/raw_sources/bank_enterprise/bank_enterprise_bank_unarrived_playbook.md", "source_type": "policy_summary", "section_title": "企业凭证真实性核验", "page_no": null, "element_type": "paragraph", "business_tags": ["bank_unarrived", "bank_enterprise", "query_reply"], "content": "银行未达账必须核对企业内部凭证、审批记录和支付指令状态。凭证缺失、审批未完成或付款指令失败时，应转人工确认。\n\n本项目抽象规则：evidence 应包含企业凭证或指令状态；无证据不得臆造到账依据。"}
{"chunk_id": "bank_enterprise_bank_unarrived_playbook_004", "source_name": "银行未达账处理公开规则摘要", "source_url": "https://www.pbc.gov.cn/eportal/fileDir/history_file/files/att_19041_2.pdf", "source_file": "data/rag/raw_sources/bank_enterprise/bank_enterprise_bank_unarrived_playbook.md", "source_type": "policy_summary", "section_title": "查询查复处理路径", "page_no": null, "element_type": "paragraph", "business_tags": ["bank_unarrived", "bank_enterprise", "query_reply"], "content": "对单笔支付状态存疑时，应通过查询查复或渠道流水追踪确认是否已发出、退回或挂账。回复内容应明确业务状态和处理原因。\n\n本项目抽象规则：`next_action` 通常为 `PENDING_HUMAN`，并提示查询查复或渠道追踪。"}
{"chunk_id": "bank_enterprise_bank_unarrived_playbook_005", "source_name": "银行未达账处理公开规则摘要", "source_url": "https://www.pbc.gov.cn/eportal/fileDir/history_file/files/att_19041_2.pdf", "source_file": "data/rag/raw_sources/bank_enterprise/bank_enterprise_bank_unarrived_playbook.md", "source_type": "policy_summary", "section_title": "后续闭环所需字段", "page_no": null, "element_type": "paragraph", "business_tags": ["bank_unarrived", "bank_enterprise", "query_reply"], "content": "银行未达账闭环至少需要企业凭证号、金额、付款账号、收款账号、交易日期和后续银行流水。缺少关键字段时，复核任务应保持未解决状态。\n\n本项目抽象规则：错误台账需保留 `flow_id`、金额和缺失侧，便于后续补证。"}
{"chunk_id": "bank_enterprise_book_unrecorded_playbook_001", "source_name": "企业未记账处理公开规则摘要", "source_url": "https://www.gov.cn/gongbao/content/2006/content_375800.htm", "source_file": "data/rag/raw_sources/bank_enterprise/bank_enterprise_book_unrecorded_playbook.md", "source_type": "policy_summary", "section_title": "银行已入企业未记", "page_no": null, "element_type": "paragraph", "business_tags": ["book_unrecorded", "bank_enterprise", "audit_trail"], "content": "银行流水已出现交易，但企业账簿没有对应分录时，应识别为企业未记账。处理时要保留银行流水号、交易时间、金额、对手方和摘要，作为后续补记账依据。\n\n本项目抽象规则：`BOOK_UNRECORDED` 对应 `BE-R006`，必须输出银行侧证据和缺失的企业账簿侧。"}
{"chunk_id": "bank_enterprise_book_unrecorded_playbook_002", "source_name": "企业未记账处理公开规则摘要", "source_url": "https://www.gov.cn/gongbao/content/2006/content_375800.htm", "source_file": "data/rag/raw_sources/bank_enterprise/bank_enterprise_book_unrecorded_playbook.md", "source_type": "policy_summary", "section_title": "银行回单和流水核对", "page_no": null, "element_type": "paragraph", "business_tags": ["book_unrecorded", "bank_enterprise", "audit_trail"], "content": "企业未记账复核应核对银行回单、流水明细和网银下载记录，确认交易真实发生。不能只凭摘要相似推断企业应补记哪一笔业务。\n\n本项目抽象规则：evidence 应引用银行侧来源文件和流水号。"}
{"chunk_id": "bank_enterprise_book_unrecorded_playbook_003", "source_name": "企业未记账处理公开规则摘要", "source_url": "https://www.gov.cn/gongbao/content/2006/content_375800.htm", "source_file": "data/rag/raw_sources/bank_enterprise/bank_enterprise_book_unrecorded_playbook.md", "source_type": "policy_summary", "section_title": "收入费用入账分类", "page_no": null, "element_type": "paragraph", "business_tags": ["book_unrecorded", "bank_enterprise", "audit_trail"], "content": "未记账交易可能属于收入、费用、退款或内部调拨。复核时需要根据摘要、对手方和用途判断会计分类，必要时交由人工确认。\n\n本项目抽象规则：AI 审计建议只提示可能分类，不直接生成会计凭证。"}
{"chunk_id": "bank_enterprise_book_unrecorded_playbook_004", "source_name": "企业未记账处理公开规则摘要", "source_url": "https://www.gov.cn/gongbao/content/2006/content_375800.htm", "source_file": "data/rag/raw_sources/bank_enterprise/bank_enterprise_book_unrecorded_playbook.md", "source_type": "policy_summary", "section_title": "重复下载和漏导入区分", "page_no": null, "element_type": "paragraph", "business_tags": ["book_unrecorded", "bank_enterprise", "audit_trail"], "content": "企业未记账有时来自账簿导入漏行，也可能是银行流水重复下载后造成的表面单边。复核需要检查批次号、导入时间和文件来源。\n\n本项目抽象规则：若存在重复下载风险，应同时检查 `DUPLICATE_BOOKING` 线索。"}
{"chunk_id": "bank_enterprise_book_unrecorded_playbook_005", "source_name": "企业未记账处理公开规则摘要", "source_url": "https://www.gov.cn/gongbao/content/2006/content_375800.htm", "source_file": "data/rag/raw_sources/bank_enterprise/bank_enterprise_book_unrecorded_playbook.md", "source_type": "policy_summary", "section_title": "补记账闭环要求", "page_no": null, "element_type": "paragraph", "business_tags": ["book_unrecorded", "bank_enterprise", "audit_trail"], "content": "企业补记账后，应将补录凭证号、处理人员、处理时间和复核结论写入差错台账。闭环记录必须能追溯到原银行流水。\n\n本项目抽象规则：错误台账保留处理建议和 RAG 来源，便于审计追溯。"}
{"chunk_id": "bank_enterprise_duplicate_booking_playbook_001", "source_name": "银企重复记账处理公开规则摘要", "source_url": "https://www.gov.cn/gongbao/content/2006/content_375800.htm", "source_file": "data/rag/raw_sources/bank_enterprise/bank_enterprise_duplicate_booking_playbook.md", "source_type": "policy_summary", "section_title": "重复记账识别", "page_no": null, "element_type": "paragraph", "business_tags": ["duplicate_booking", "bank_enterprise", "audit_trail"], "content": "同一业务在企业账簿中出现多笔金额、日期和对手方高度相同的分录，或银行流水被重复导入形成多条候选记录，应识别为重复记账风险。\n\n本项目抽象规则：`DUPLICATE_BOOKING` 对应 `BE-R008`，需要列出重复候选流水和重复依据。"}
{"chunk_id": "bank_enterprise_duplicate_booking_playbook_002", "source_name": "银企重复记账处理公开规则摘要", "source_url": "https://www.gov.cn/gongbao/content/2006/content_375800.htm", "source_file": "data/rag/raw_sources/bank_enterprise/bank_enterprise_duplicate_booking_playbook.md", "source_type": "policy_summary", "section_title": "流水号和凭证号去重", "page_no": null, "element_type": "paragraph", "business_tags": ["duplicate_booking", "bank_enterprise", "audit_trail"], "content": "重复记账判断应优先核对银行流水号、企业凭证号、批次号和原始文件行号。只有金额相同但流水号不同，不足以直接认定重复。\n\n本项目抽象规则：evidence 需要包含可追溯的唯一键或重复候选集合。"}
{"chunk_id": "bank_enterprise_duplicate_booking_playbook_003", "source_name": "银企重复记账处理公开规则摘要", "source_url": "https://www.gov.cn/gongbao/content/2006/content_375800.htm", "source_file": "data/rag/raw_sources/bank_enterprise/bank_enterprise_duplicate_booking_playbook.md", "source_type": "policy_summary", "section_title": "批量导入重复", "page_no": null, "element_type": "paragraph", "business_tags": ["duplicate_booking", "bank_enterprise", "audit_trail"], "content": "企业账簿批量导入失败重试、重复上传或跨系统同步，可能造成同一业务被记入多次。复核时应检查导入批次、文件名和导入时间。\n\n本项目抽象规则：审计意见应提示核对批次和文件来源。"}
{"chunk_id": "bank_enterprise_duplicate_booking_playbook_004", "source_name": "银企重复记账处理公开规则摘要", "source_url": "https://www.gov.cn/gongbao/content/2006/content_375800.htm", "source_file": "data/rag/raw_sources/bank_enterprise/bank_enterprise_duplicate_booking_playbook.md", "source_type": "policy_summary", "section_title": "冲正与重复的区别", "page_no": null, "element_type": "paragraph", "business_tags": ["duplicate_booking", "bank_enterprise", "audit_trail"], "content": "冲正或退款会形成方向相反的关联流水，不应简单归为重复记账。重复记账通常表现为同方向、同金额、同对手方的多条记录。\n\n本项目抽象规则：摘要含冲正、退款或撤销时，应优先触发摘要差异或追溯判断。"}
{"chunk_id": "bank_enterprise_duplicate_booking_playbook_005", "source_name": "银企重复记账处理公开规则摘要", "source_url": "https://www.gov.cn/gongbao/content/2006/content_375800.htm", "source_file": "data/rag/raw_sources/bank_enterprise/bank_enterprise_duplicate_booking_playbook.md", "source_type": "policy_summary", "section_title": "重复处理闭环", "page_no": null, "element_type": "paragraph", "business_tags": ["duplicate_booking", "bank_enterprise", "audit_trail"], "content": "确认重复后，需要标注保留记录和冲销记录，并记录处理原因、审批人和处理时间。未确认前应保持待人工复核，避免误删真实交易。\n\n本项目抽象规则：AI 只给出重复风险和候选证据，不直接删除或冲销账务。"}
{"chunk_id": "bank_enterprise_narrative_mismatch_playbook_001", "source_name": "银企对账摘要户名差异处理公开规则摘要", "source_url": "https://www.pbc.gov.cn/eportal/fileDir/history_file/files/att_19041_2.pdf", "source_file": "data/rag/raw_sources/bank_enterprise/bank_enterprise_narrative_mismatch_playbook.md", "source_type": "policy_summary", "section_title": "摘要和户名不一致", "page_no": null, "element_type": "paragraph", "business_tags": ["narrative_name_mismatch", "bank_enterprise", "query_reply"], "content": "银行流水与企业账簿金额一致，但摘要、用途、对手户名或客户简称不一致时，应视为业务要素差异。该类差异不能仅凭金额一致自动通过，需要保留差异字段和原始来源。\n\n本项目抽象规则：`NARRATIVE_NAME_MISMATCH` 对应 `BE-R004`，审计输出需要说明摘要或户名差异点。"}
{"chunk_id": "bank_enterprise_narrative_mismatch_playbook_002", "source_name": "银企对账摘要户名差异处理公开规则摘要", "source_url": "https://www.pbc.gov.cn/eportal/fileDir/history_file/files/att_19041_2.pdf", "source_file": "data/rag/raw_sources/bank_enterprise/bank_enterprise_narrative_mismatch_playbook.md", "source_type": "policy_summary", "section_title": "别名简称映射核验", "page_no": null, "element_type": "paragraph", "business_tags": ["narrative_name_mismatch", "bank_enterprise", "query_reply"], "content": "同一交易对手可能存在公司全称、简称、门店名或平台商户名。核验时可以使用已维护的别名映射，但必须记录映射来源和匹配依据。\n\n本项目抽象规则：没有可信别名证据时，不能把户名差异自动判定为可通过。"}
{"chunk_id": "bank_enterprise_narrative_mismatch_playbook_003", "source_name": "银企对账摘要户名差异处理公开规则摘要", "source_url": "https://www.pbc.gov.cn/eportal/fileDir/history_file/files/att_19041_2.pdf", "source_file": "data/rag/raw_sources/bank_enterprise/bank_enterprise_narrative_mismatch_playbook.md", "source_type": "policy_summary", "section_title": "冲正退款摘要识别", "page_no": null, "element_type": "paragraph", "business_tags": ["narrative_name_mismatch", "bank_enterprise", "query_reply"], "content": "摘要中出现冲正、红冲、退款、撤销等字样时，即使金额接近，也应优先判断是否为原交易的反向处理。需要关联原交易号、原日期和冲正流水号。\n\n本项目抽象规则：摘要含冲正线索时触发提取或追溯证据，避免把反向流水误当正常收付款。"}
{"chunk_id": "bank_enterprise_narrative_mismatch_playbook_004", "source_name": "银企对账摘要户名差异处理公开规则摘要", "source_url": "https://www.pbc.gov.cn/eportal/fileDir/history_file/files/att_19041_2.pdf", "source_file": "data/rag/raw_sources/bank_enterprise/bank_enterprise_narrative_mismatch_playbook.md", "source_type": "policy_summary", "section_title": "用途字段和合同信息核对", "page_no": null, "element_type": "paragraph", "business_tags": ["narrative_name_mismatch", "bank_enterprise", "query_reply"], "content": "企业账簿常以合同号、发票号或订单号入账，银行流水可能只包含付款用途。用途字段差异需要结合合同、订单或查询查复记录确认。\n\n本项目抽象规则：evidence 应体现用途、合同号或订单号来源，缺证据时进入人工复核。"}
{"chunk_id": "bank_enterprise_narrative_mismatch_playbook_005", "source_name": "银企对账摘要户名差异处理公开规则摘要", "source_url": "https://www.pbc.gov.cn/eportal/fileDir/history_file/files/att_19041_2.pdf", "source_file": "data/rag/raw_sources/bank_enterprise/bank_enterprise_narrative_mismatch_playbook.md", "source_type": "policy_summary", "section_title": "摘要噪声和有效关键词", "page_no": null, "element_type": "paragraph", "business_tags": ["narrative_name_mismatch", "bank_enterprise", "query_reply"], "content": "银行渠道会追加渠道名、批次号、终端号等系统噪声。复核摘要差异时应区分系统噪声和业务关键字，避免因无关前后缀造成误判。\n\n本项目抽象规则：审计建议可以提示忽略渠道噪声，但必须保留原始摘要文本。"}
{"chunk_id": "pbc_epayment_guideline_001", "source_name": "中国人民银行《电子支付指引（第一号）》公开条款摘录", "source_url": "https://www.gov.cn/gongbao/content/2006/content_375800.htm", "source_file": "data/rag/raw_sources/bank_enterprise/pbc_epayment_guideline.md", "source_type": "html_excerpt", "section_title": "电子支付差错登记和审计留痕", "page_no": null, "element_type": "paragraph", "business_tags": ["audit_trail", "error_handling"], "content": "电子支付业务出现差错时，应保留可追溯的处理记录。差错台账需要覆盖差错发生时间、差错内容、处理部门或人员、客户资料、影响或损失、差错原因、处理结果等字段。\n\n本项目抽象规则：`audit_trail` 场景必须保留原始异常、处理过程、处理结论和规则来源；没有来源依据时不能生成自动审计结论。"}
{"chunk_id": "pbc_epayment_guideline_002", "source_name": "中国人民银行《电子支付指引（第一号）》公开条款摘录", "source_url": "https://www.gov.cn/gongbao/content/2006/content_375800.htm", "source_file": "data/rag/raw_sources/bank_enterprise/pbc_epayment_guideline.md", "source_type": "html_excerpt", "section_title": "交易记录保存要求", "page_no": null, "element_type": "paragraph", "business_tags": ["audit_trail", "error_handling"], "content": "电子支付交易记录和安全校验记录应妥善保存，便于后续查询、追溯和审计。对账系统中的异常处理结果应能关联到原始交易、异常类型和处理依据。\n\n本项目抽象规则：差错明细、RAG 命中来源和后续审计建议需要绑定同一个 `task_id` 与 `flow_id`。"}
{"chunk_id": "pbc_small_payment_query_reply_001", "source_name": "小额支付系统业务处理手续公开材料摘录", "source_url": "https://www.pbc.gov.cn/eportal/fileDir/history_file/files/att_19041_2.pdf", "source_file": "data/rag/raw_sources/bank_enterprise/pbc_small_payment_query_reply.md", "source_type": "pdf_excerpt", "section_title": "单笔业务查询查复", "page_no": null, "element_type": "paragraph", "business_tags": ["single_side_missing", "query_reply", "error_handling"], "content": "小额支付系统业务处理中，对存在疑问或差错的单笔业务，需要通过查询查复机制核实。查询查复强调发现疑问应查询，收到查询应回复，回复内容应详细、明确。\n\n本项目抽象规则：`SINGLE_SIDE_MISSING` 代表银行端或清算端只有一侧存在流水，不能直接自动平账，应先进入待人工复核或后续追溯查询。"}
{"chunk_id": "pbc_small_payment_query_reply_002", "source_name": "小额支付系统业务处理手续公开材料摘录", "source_url": "https://www.pbc.gov.cn/eportal/fileDir/history_file/files/att_19041_2.pdf", "source_file": "data/rag/raw_sources/bank_enterprise/pbc_small_payment_query_reply.md", "source_type": "pdf_excerpt", "section_title": "原始凭证和业务要素核对", "page_no": null, "element_type": "paragraph", "business_tags": ["single_side_missing", "query_reply", "error_handling"], "content": "涉及业务要素更正或差错确认时，应以原始凭证、原始交易记录和支付业务要素为依据。系统不能只根据摘要相似或单侧金额推断最终处理结论。\n\n本项目抽象规则：单边缺失、跨日切和疑似漏记账需要保留原始流水号、金额、交易时间、渠道和来源文件。"}
{"chunk_id": "unionpay_reconciliation_faq_001", "source_name": "银联一窗办清算对账公开 FAQ 摘录", "source_url": "https://pcs.unionpay.com/ycb/pcweb/NEWbzzx/cjwt/ywcp/jcyw/dj/FKYW/art/2024/art_bc798a9bee334e5d8a19286b66bbfe61.html", "source_file": "data/rag/raw_sources/bank_enterprise/unionpay_reconciliation_faq.md", "source_type": "html_excerpt", "section_title": "清算文件流水与资金核对不平", "page_no": null, "element_type": "paragraph", "business_tags": ["amount_mismatch", "single_side_missing", "clearing_file_exception"], "content": "公开 FAQ 提到，清算文件流水与资金核对不平、对账文件缺失、流水缺失等问题属于清算文件异常处理范围，需要通过指定服务路径提交处理。\n\n本项目抽象规则：`AMOUNT_MISMATCH` 表示同一 `flow_id` 在银行端和清算端均存在，但标准金额不一致；系统应保留银行端金额、清算端金额和差异金额，并进入待 AI 审计。"}
{"chunk_id": "unionpay_reconciliation_faq_002", "source_name": "银联一窗办清算对账公开 FAQ 摘录", "source_url": "https://pcs.unionpay.com/ycb/pcweb/NEWbzzx/cjwt/ywcp/jcyw/dj/FKYW/art/2024/art_bc798a9bee334e5d8a19286b66bbfe61.html", "source_file": "data/rag/raw_sources/bank_enterprise/unionpay_reconciliation_faq.md", "source_type": "html_excerpt", "section_title": "对账文件或流水缺失", "page_no": null, "element_type": "paragraph", "business_tags": ["amount_mismatch", "single_side_missing", "clearing_file_exception"], "content": "对账文件缺失或流水缺失会导致双端无法闭环核验。此类异常不能用单侧数据直接确认平账，需要保留缺失侧、来源文件和处理路径。\n\n本项目抽象规则：`SINGLE_SIDE_MISSING` 需要输出缺失方向、已有侧金额和来源依据；后续可进入查询查复、T+1 追溯或人工复核。"}
